{"title":"小站春早","authors":["汤世杰"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":12,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小站春早"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昆明铁路分局  汤世杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河的水，亮了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝头的芽，醒了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只一夜，春风浩荡过山岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把小站的信号灯也染绿了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天呵，在站房里喧闹——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电话机，叮叮叫；红绿灯，啪啪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天呵，追着车轮飞跑——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手旗飞，燕展翅；哨音脆，车呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……昨晚，党支书开会回站来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带回一束山花，几捆书报；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更是他，传达了华主席的重要讲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时，北京的春风吹遍山坳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵，听咱大声报告——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里小站春来早！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明媚春光，映了红心，再染绿水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里春色，先上眉梢，才挂树梢……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}